nodes.text: Dorin Bell was a male human scientist who served the Galactic Empire. In 7 BBY, Bell was the first target for Jyn Erso to assassinate on the planet Horuz. However, he was killed not by Erso's weapon, but by a grenade from a trap set up by the Partisans in case of Erso's failure.
